  "markdown": "[Skip to main content](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/%C2%A32B-and-what-actually-matters#main-content)\n[](https://universalquantum.com/)\n## Main navigation\n  * [Who we are](https://universalquantum.com/who-we-are)\n  * [What we do](https://universalquantum.com/what-we-do)\n  * [Working here](https://universalquantum.com/working-here)\n  * Knowledge hub\n    * [News & Blog](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/news-blog)\n    * [Technical Resources](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/technical-resources)\n  * [Contact us](https://universalquantum.com/contact-us)\n\n\nToggle menu\n  * [En](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/%C2%A32B-and-what-actually-matters)\n  * [De](https://universalquantum.com/de/node/178)\n\n\n## Main navigation\n  * [Who we are](https://universalquantum.com/who-we-are)\n  * [What we do](https://universalquantum.com/what-we-do)\n  * [Working here](https://universalquantum.com/working-here)\n  * [Knowledge hub](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub)\n    * [News & Blog](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/news-blog)\n    * [Technical Resources](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/technical-resources)\n  * [Contact us](https://universalquantum.com/contact-us)\n\n\n[Privacy](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/%C2%A32B-and-what-actually-matters)  \n[Cookies](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/%C2%A32B-and-what-actually-matters)\n\u00a9 2026 Universal Quantum Ltd.\n  * [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/universal-quantum)\n  * [X](https://x.com/universalquant)\n\n\n# Podcast: \u00a32B and What Actually Matters\n![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/banner_dekstop/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?h=e55433bc&itok=Es3zYtGf)\nDate **30 Mar 2026**\nCategory **\nPodcasts\n**\nThis episode explores the UK government\u2019s \u00a32 billion commitment to quantum technologies, and what it signals about the next phase of the field. It examines how funding is being allocated, the role of government procurement, and how defined missions are shaping direction across computing, sensing, and networks.\nThe discussion also addresses common misconceptions around quantum computing, including what a quantum computer actually is, where it is likely to deliver value, and where expectations are overstated. It places the UK\u2019s approach in a global context, comparing investment, capability, and long term strategy.\nTaken together, the episode provides a grounded view of how UK quantum is moving into a more structured phase of development, from research programmes to deployment, and what that means for industry, jobs, and economic impact over time.\n[ ![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-05/Logo%202.jpg?h=32ebe3b7&itok=gxN2Nc4j) Podcast:The Quantum Rivalry of Schr\u00f6dinger & Heisenberg Explore the fascinating parallels between heated rivalries in sports and the intense debates in quantum physics, focusing on Schr\u00f6dinger and Heisenberg. ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-quantum-rivalry-of-schr%C3%B6dinger-and-eisenberg)\n[ ![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=c05c9e62&itok=wV06w5AW) Universal Quantum appoints Freeke Heijman as Senior European Advisor Universal Quantum, the UK based company building the world's most scalable quantum computers, today announced the appointment of Freeke Heijman as Senior European Advisor. ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/universal-quantum-appoints-Freeke-Heijman-as-senior-european-advisor)\n[ ![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=d0e75635&itok=1VzwC13Q) Podcast: The Wiring Problem in Large-Scale Quantum Computers This episode explores the challenges of wiring and control systems in large-scale quantum computers, drawing parallels with classical electronics and physics labs. ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-wiring-problem-in-large-scale-quantum-computers)\n[ ![UQ](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-03/1774259818783.jpeg?h=b67ea17b&itok=dPElSwQ-) Universal Quantum selected for Tech Nation Future Fifty 2026 Universal Quantum has been selected to join Tech Nation\u2019s Future Fifty 2026 cohort, the UK\u2019s flagship programme supporting high growth scaleups. ](https://universalquantum.com/knowledge-hub/universal-quantum-selected-for-tech-nation-fifty-2026)\n  * [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/universal-quantum)\n  * [X](https://x.com/universalquant)\n\n\n## Secondary menu\n  * [Contact us](https://universalquantum.com/contact-us)\n\n\n[Privacy](https://universalquantum.com/privacy-policy)\n\u00a9 2026 Universal Quantum Ltd.  \n\n![](https://universalquantum.com/sites/default/files/inline-images/footer.png)\n",
