le\">     <div class=\"node__banner node__banner--article banner\">\n      <div class=\"banner__title\">\n        <div class=\"wrapper\"><h1 class=\"h2\">Podcast: \u00a32B and What Actually Matters</h1></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"banner__image\">\n        <div class=\"field field--image field--label-hidden field__item\">\n              <picture>\n                  <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_dekstop/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?h=e55433bc&amp;itok=Es3zYtGf 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 1024px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1920\" height=\"822\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/portrait_mobile/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?itok=NFASvZAG 1x\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"650\" height=\"650\">\n                  <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_dekstop/public/2026-03/Logo%202.jpg?h=e55433bc&amp;itok=Es3zYtGf\" width=\"1920\" height=\"822\" alt=\"UQ\" class=\"round\">\n\n  </picture>\n\n  </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"node__content node__content--article wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"node__meta stack--single wrapper wrapper--small\">\n        <div class=\"meta\">\n          <span class=\"meta__label\">Date<span>\n          <strong class=\"meta__content text-upper\">30 Mar 2026</strong>\n        </span></span></div>\n                  <div class=\"meta\">\n            <span class=\"meta__label\">Category<span>\n            <strong class=\"meta__content text-upper\"><div class=\"field field--tags field--label-hidden field--entity-reference field__item field__items\">\n          Podcasts  </div>\n</strong>\n          </span></span></div>\n              </div>\n      <div class=\"field field--components field--label-hidden field--entity-reference-revisions field__items\">\n          <div class=\"paragraph paragraph--text paragraph--default wrapper wrapper--small content\">\n          <div class=\"clearfix field--formatted field field--text-formatted field--label-hidden field--text-long field__item\">\n          <p class=\"body-large\">This episode explores the UK government\u2019s \u00a32 billion commitment to quantum technologies, and what it signals about the next phase of the field. It examines how funding is being allocated, the role of government procurement, and how defined missions are shaping direction across computing, sensing, and networks.</p><p class=\"body-large\">The discussion also addresses common misconceptions around quantum computing, including what a quantum computer actually is, where it is likely to deliver value, and where expectations are overstated. It places the UK\u2019s approach in a global context, comparing investment, capability, and long term strategy.</p><p class=\"body-large\">Taken together, the episode provides a grounded view of how UK quantum is moving into a more structured phase of development, from research programmes to deployment, and what that means for industry, jobs, and economic impact over time.</p>  </div>\n\n      </div>\n  <div class=\"paragraph paragraph--text paragraph--default wrapper wrapper--small content\">\n          <div class=\"clearfix field--formatted field field--text-formatted field--label-hidden field--text-long field__item\">\n          <p><iframe style=\"border-radius:12px;\" data-testid=\"embed-iframe\" src=\"https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/0RItURKPjfYORGTfgfCvwS?utm_source=generator\" width=\"100%\" height=\"352\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>  </div>\n\n      </div>\n</div>\n\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n </div>\n    <div class=\"page__secondary\">   <div class=\"block block--view block--news-and-blog-block-1\">   \n    \n        <div class=\"view-grid view view--news_and_blog view--display-block-1 js-view-dom-id-e06c592b4c28e58adedabba4131b14b620a088e3e444023534b824b1fc79e880\">\n  <div class=\"wrapper\">\n    \n        \n            \n          <div class=\"view__content\">\n            <div class=\"view__row\">\n \n\n\n  <article class=\"node node--teaser node--type-article\">\n    <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-quantum-rivalry-of-schr%C3%B6dinger-and-eisenberg\" class=\"bare-link stack--single\" rel=\"bookmark\">\n      <div class=\"field field--image field--label-hidden field__item\">\n              <picture>\n                  <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-05/Logo%202.jpg?h=32ebe3b7&amp;itok=gxN2Nc4j 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 1024px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_mobile/public/2026-05/Logo%202.jpg?h=32ebe3b7&amp;itok=gsaEcn0r 1x\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\">\n                  <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-05/Logo%202.jpg?h=32ebe3b7&amp;itok=gxN2Nc4j\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\" alt=\"UQ\" class=\"round\">\n\n  </picture>\n\n  </div>\n\n      <h3 class=\"teaser__title\">Podcast:The Quantum Rivalry of Schr\u00f6dinger &amp; Heisenberg</h3>\n      <div class=\"teaser__content\">\n        <div class=\"clearfix field--formatted field field--preview-text field--label-hidden field--text-long field__item\">\n          <p><span class=\"sc-kUnTIk zeTzM text-pink\" data-slate-node=\"text\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-slate-string=\"true\">Explore the fascinating parallels between heated rivalries in sports and the intense debates in quantum physics, focusing on Schr\u00f6dinger and Heisenberg.</span></p>  </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </a>\n  </article>\n</div>\n    <div class=\"view__row\">\n \n\n\n  <article class=\"node node--teaser node--type-article\">\n    <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/universal-quantum-appoints-Freeke-Heijman-as-senior-european-advisor\" class=\"bare-link stack--single\" rel=\"bookmark\">\n      <div class=\"field field--image field--label-hidden field__item\">\n              <picture>\n                  <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=c05c9e62&amp;itok=wV06w5AW 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 1024px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_mobile/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=c05c9e62&amp;itok=GqfA8Xjr 1x\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"533\" height=\"533\">\n                  <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-05/52995517310_bba4d9d357_c.jpg?h=c05c9e62&amp;itok=wV06w5AW\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\" alt=\"UQ\" class=\"round\">\n\n  </picture>\n\n  </div>\n\n      <h3 class=\"teaser__title\">Universal Quantum appoints Freeke Heijman as Senior European Advisor</h3>\n      <div class=\"teaser__content\">\n        <div class=\"clearfix field--formatted field field--preview-text field--label-hidden field--text-long field__item\">\n          <p><span class=\"text-pink\">Universal Quantum, the UK based company building the world's most scalable quantum computers, today announced the appointment of Freeke Heijman as Senior European Advisor.</span></p>  </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </a>\n  </article>\n</div>\n    <div class=\"view__row\">\n \n\n\n  <article class=\"node node--teaser node--type-article\">\n    <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/podcast/the-wiring-problem-in-large-scale-quantum-computers\" class=\"bare-link stack--single\" rel=\"bookmark\">\n      <div class=\"field field--image field--label-hidden field__item\">\n              <picture>\n                  <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=d0e75635&amp;itok=1VzwC13Q 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 1024px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_mobile/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=d0e75635&amp;itok=H9kGYiNn 1x\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\">\n                  <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-04/Logo%202.jpg?h=d0e75635&amp;itok=1VzwC13Q\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\" alt=\"UQ\" class=\"round\">\n\n  </picture>\n\n  </div>\n\n      <h3 class=\"teaser__title\">Podcast: The Wiring Problem in Large-Scale Quantum Computers</h3>\n      <div class=\"teaser__content\">\n        <div class=\"clearfix field--formatted field field--preview-text field--label-hidden field--text-long field__item\">\n          <p><span class=\"sc-fzUa-dk gFqrs text-pink\" data-slate-node=\"text\" data-slate-leaf=\"true\" data-slate-string=\"true\">This episode explores the challenges of wiring and control systems in large-scale quantum computers, drawing parallels with classical electronics and physics labs.</span></p>  </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </a>\n  </article>\n</div>\n    <div class=\"view__row\">\n \n\n\n  <article class=\"node node--teaser node--type-article\">\n    <a href=\"/knowledge-hub/universal-quantum-selected-for-tech-nation-fifty-2026\" class=\"bare-link stack--single\" rel=\"bookmark\">\n      <div class=\"field field--image field--label-hidden field__item\">\n              <picture>\n                  <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-03/1774259818783.jpeg?h=b67ea17b&amp;itok=dPElSwQ- 1x\" media=\"all and (min-width: 1024px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\">\n              <source srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/banner_mobile/public/2026-03/1774259818783.jpeg?h=b67ea17b&amp;itok=jpOgEJn- 1x\" type=\"image/jpeg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\">\n                  <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/cta_desktop/public/2026-03/1774259818783.jpeg?h=b67ea17b&amp;itok=dPElSwQ-\" width=\"810\" height=\"810\" alt=\"UQ\" class=\"round\">\n\n  </picture>\n\n  </div>\n\n      <h3 class=\"teaser__title\">Universal Quantum selected for Tech Nation Future Fifty 2026</h3>\n      <div class=\"teaser__content\">\n        <div class=\"clearfix field--formatted field field--preview-text field--label-hidden field--text-long field__item\">\n          <p><span class=\"text-pink\">Universal Quantum has been selected to join Tech Nation\u2019s Future Fifty 2026 cohort, the UK\u2019s flagship programme supporting high growth scaleups.</span></p>  </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </a>\n  </article>\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n    \n                      </div>\n</div>\n\n\n  </div>\n </div>\n  </main>\n  <footer class=\"page__footer card card--footer spacer-huge text-white\">\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      <div class=\"footer__first\">   <div class=\"block block--footer-logo\">   \n    \n      <!-- Field: body -->\n<svg class=\"footer-logo\" width=\"200\" height=\"171\" viewBox=\"0 0 229 171\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M110.568 48.0758C110.568 50.2877 108.778 52.0808 106.57 52.0808L63.4636 52.0808C61.2552 52.0808 59.4649 50.2877 59.4649 48.0758L59.4649 4.98233C59.4649 2.77044 61.2552 0.977352 63.4636 0.977352L106.57 0.977356C108.778 0.977356 110.568 2.77045 110.568 4.98233L110.568 48.0758Z\" fill=\"#FF006A\"></path><path d=\"M228.5 107.04C228.5 109.252 226.71 111.045 224.501 111.045L181.395 111.045C179.187 111.045 177.397 109.252 177.397 107.04L177.397 63.9467C177.397 61.7348 179.187 59.9417 181.395 59.9417L224.501 59.9417C226.71 59.9417 228.5 61.7348 228.5 63.9467L228.5 107.04Z\" fill=\"#FF006A\"></path><path d=\"M51.6035 107.04C51.6035 109.252 49.8104 111.045 47.5985 111.045L34.9428 111.045C15.9206 111.045 0.500062 95.6246 0.500064 76.6024L0.500065 63.9467C0.500065 61.7348 2.29315 59.9417 4.50504 59.9417L47.5985 59.9417C49.8104 59.9417 51.6035 61.7348 51.6035 63.9467L51.6035 107.04Z\" fill=\"#FF006A\"></path><path d=\"M0.5 4.98153C0.5 2.76965 2.29309 0.976562 4.50497 0.976562L17.1607 0.976562C36.1829 0.976562 51.6035 16.3971 51.6035 35.4193V48.075C51.6035 50.2869 49.8104 52.08 47.5985 52.08L4.50497 52.08C2.29309 52.08 0.5 50.2869 0.5 4